# .understandignore — focus the Understand Anything scan on sui-pilot's OWN code,
# not the 750+ vendored third-party doc pages bundled in this repo.
# Syntax: same as .gitignore.

# --- Vendored documentation mirrors (bulk of the repo, not our code) ---
.sui-docs/
.walrus-docs/
.seal-docs/
.move-book-docs/
.ts-sdk-docs/
.sui-prover-docs/

# --- Belt-and-suspenders secret exclusions ---
# (git ls-files --exclude-standard already drops gitignored files, but these
#  also cover any *tracked* secret and protect non-git scans. Reusable template.)
*.env
.env*
!*.env.example
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
.secrets/
id_rsa*
*.mnemonic
